text: Irene Viaene (born 7 December 1949) is an Argentine alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Argentina Category:Alpine skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Corrientes Province
